data.name: TextChangelog.Text
data.value:
Changed alot of code for faster guild adding in the GUI, Fixed a bunch of issues and adding a warning for bad token and making commands always edit in DMs so users dont get 2 messages at once
More GUI changes including command groups, help menus, selfbot folder button, self clean command and an app icon
Finally fixed the freezing issue and fixed the emoji count in self guild
Few changes to the GUI, disabled some elements based on the actions and made the embed text boxes clear all
Fixed a bunch of stuff, tested all commands and added TotalUptime and TotalRuns on self uptime
Added more commands uptime/guild/neko
Fixed showing embed color and favorite color
Custom themes added
Major overhaul of the GUI
